result.title: Event Cluster 1
result.description: The Event Clusters will include high-level events and workshops related to EU-China cooperation on sustainable urbanization, in which URBAN-EU-CHINA functions either as host, co-organisor or representative. There will be 2 Event Clusters per year (1/year in Europe, 1/year in China) related to meetings of the Consortium, Management Board and Advisory Board, including open events and WP/Task-related activities. In addition, Event Clusters will encompass Authorities Workshops, Industry Workshops, Research and Innovation Workshops, Cities Workshops, and a Matching Cities / Powerhouse Demonstration Projects Awards Ceremony. This deliverable is led by CAUPD and EUR, and all Consortium Partners will contribute with their extensive partner networks and events.

result.description: The Event Clusters will include high-level events and workshops related to EU-China cooperation on sustainable urbanization, in which URBAN-EU-CHINA functions either as host, co-organisor or representative. In addition, Event Clusters will encompass Authorities Workshops, Industry Workshops, Research and Innovation Workshops, Cities Workshops, and a Matching Cities / Powerhouse Demonstration Projects Awards Ceremony. This deliverable is led by CAUPD and EUR, and all Consortium Partners will contribute with their extensive partner networks and events.
